%N A397081 Expansion of g.f. (Sum_{j>=1} x^j/(1-x^j))^2 * Product_{k>=1} (1+x^k)^k.
%F A397081 a(n) ~ exp(3^(4/3) * zeta(3)^(1/3) * n^(2/3) / 2^(4/3)) * (log(2*n/(3*zeta(3))) + 3*gamma)^2 / (27 * 2^(1/12) * sqrt(Pi*zeta(3))), where gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant A001620.
%t A397081 nmax = 40; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[x^j/(1-x^j), {j, 1, nmax}]^2 * Product[(1+x^k)^k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]
